County: Source: Point-in-Time Counts from ServicePoint as reported by CoCs, 2015

*In these counties the PIT count was reported to OHCS in the same format that was submitted to HUD. HUD does not allow CoCs to report missing age, gender, ethnicity, or race data and provides a PIT Count Data Extrapolation Tool to allow CoCs to extrapolate estimates for the missing data. For all other counties the missing data is included here.
